# Cybersecurity Home Lab

A personal lab environment built using GitHub Codespaces to practice
penetration testing, web application security, and defensive security.

## Lab Setup
- Platform: GitHub Codespaces (Ubuntu Linux)
- Vulnerable targets: DVWA, OWASP Juice Shop
- Tools: Nmap, Gobuster, Nikto, SQLMap, Hydra, Burp Suite, Splunk

## Contents

### /notes
Command references and concept notes built during training.

### /writeups
TryHackMe and HackTheBox room writeups with methodology and commands.

### /reports
Formal penetration test reports written against lab targets.

### /scripts
Custom scripts written to automate tasks.

